<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.4.6">
<l>pārā rulakum paṉimāl varaiyum kaṭalum cuṭaru mivaiyuṇ ṭumeṉak</l>
<l>kārā teṉaniṉ ṟavaṉem perumā ṉalainī rulakuk karacā kiyavap</l>
<l>pērā ṉaimuṉin tamuṉik karaiyaṉ piṟaril lainuṉak keṉumel laiyiṉāṉ</l>
<l>nīrārp peyarāṉ neṭumā lavaṉuk kiṭammā malaiyā vatunīr malaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place for tall Māl, the one whose name includes [the word] water,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one who, even though having consumed</l>
<l>The earthly world, great snowy peaks, the sea, and the sun, continued to say,</l>
<l rend="indent">“It’s not enough for me,”</l>
<l>Our great lord, king of sages who raged against that great one</l>
<l rend="indent">who had become king of the roiling sea[-encircled] world,</l>
<l>The one whose measure is [such that] there are no others [that compare] to you</l>
<l rend="indent">even a little, is the great mountain, namely Nīrmalai.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
